The paper discusses approaches for Open Information Extraction, which involves extracting information from unstructured text. This task is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and databases (cs.DB). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
